                            <p>16.2 A notice or other communication shall be deemed to have been received:</p>
                            <p>16.2.1 if delivered personally, when left at the address referred to in clause 19.4; if sent by prepaid first class post or recorded delivery, at 9.00 am on the second Business Day after posting; if delivered by commercial courier, on the date and at the time that the courier's delivery receipt is signed;  </p>
                            <p>16.2.2 if sent by email, at the time of transmission  </p>
